import axiosInstance from './axios-connetion'

export default function listings(filters){

  const type = filter.type
  const area = filters.area
  const price = filters.price
  const view = filter.view
  const lat_coord = filter.lat_coord
  const lng_coord = filter.lng_coord
  const bedrooms = filter.bedrooms
  const livingrooms = filter.livingrooms

  axiosInstance
        .post(`listings/query/`, {
            type: type,
            area: area,
            price: price,
            view: view,
            lat_coord: lat_coord,
            lng_coord: lng_coord,
            bedrooms: bedrooms,
            livingrooms: livingrooms
        })
        .then((res) => {
            console.log(res)
        })
        .catch((err)=>{
            console.log("could not request from server")
        })
}
